body:
Same here. Windows 10, Truffle 4.1.8:

1) truffle init

2) create a simple test sol with: import "truffle/Assert.sol";

3) truffle.cmd compile

4) Error: Could not find truffle/Assert.sol from any sources;

@cgewecke I guess I know exactly what the problem was (at least at my side).

I had misplaced the Test .sol into the "contracts/" folder. When it was properly placed in "test" folder - everything went fine.

Guess worth mentioning if someone else repeats my silly mistake.
